{"tid":2421406,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"海怡半島1樓750萬成交 　代理：「同瞓街冇分別」","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T13:05:51.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"337e8ba780b4381cc64b49f48baab4d411e6dd89","tid":2421406,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kIUldK_pNvmLIYVISRLsOcmRQuQ=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EWVJRJUBKRFH7J5T3EUAGRIYIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkIUldK_pNvmLIYVISRLsOcmRQuQ%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEWVJRJUBKRFH7J5T3EUAGRIYIA.jpg&h=f8aeddf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海怡半島低層戶對正馬路，車聲嘈音較大。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n樓市剛性需求強勁，連凶宅同層及1樓單位也獲吸納。市場消息指，鴨脷洲海怡半島20座1樓單位，實用面積592方呎，兩房加士多房間隔，成交價750萬元，呎價12,669元，較銀行估價低約3%。有區內代理指，由於是最低層1樓，貼近馬路，車聲嘈音較大，形容「同瞓街冇分別」，故價錢特平，屬市場最平放盤，其他放盤叫價全部800萬元以上，買家為求平價上車，質素次要，猶如大旺市盲搶樓。<br />\n<br />\n凶宅同層齊頭1,000萬做到「林鄭Plan」<br />\n海怡半島交投熾熱，單日錄得3宗成交，除上述1樓單位外，另一宗為9座高層D室，屬凶宅同層戶，實用面積640方呎，三房間隔，以1,000萬元沽出，可承造最高八成按揭，坊間俗稱「林鄭Plan」，較剛以1,148萬元成交的9座高層C室同類單位賣平逾一成。<br />\n另沙田第一城17座低層G室，實用面積327方呎，兩房間隔，屬凶宅同層戶，成交價520萬元，呎價15,902元，低市價約半成。據代理提供資料，沙田第一城52幢住宅物業中，有超過40間凶宅，凶案種類涵蓋吊頸、跳樓、腐屍、燒炭、煤氣爆炸等。其中17座佔四間最多，包括在2008年曾發生轟動三屍自殺案的單位。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210224/CPHKK7JKXNGGFDEZBSGKL4S2JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210224%2FCPHKK7JKXNGGFDEZBSGKL4S2JU%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8M5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=8b261db2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210224%2FCPHKK7JKXNGGFDEZBSGKL4S2JU%2F&h=24046ca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210224/CPHKK7JKXNGGFDEZBSGKL4S2JU/</a>"},{"pid":"eb14aacd06baf9d92711e9408